---
import Base from "@/layouts/Base.astro";
import ServiceSlider from "@/components/ServiceSlider.astro";
import Donationcard from "../../layouts/components/donationcard.astro";

import { SEO } from "astro-seo";


---

<SEO
  title="Edhi Foundation Refugees Assistance - Support Refugees"
  description="Support Edhi Foundation's Refugees Assistance services. Help provide aid and support to refugees in need."
  canonical={Astro.request.url}
  openGraph={{
    basic: {
      title: "Edhi Foundation Refugees Assistance - Support Refugees",
      type: "A type.",
      image: "https://edhiuk.org/images/logo.jpg",
    
    }
  }}
  twitter={{
    creator: "@jonasmerlins1"
  }}
  extend={{
    // extending the default link tags
    link: [{ rel: "icon", href: "/favicon.png" }],
    // extending the default meta tags
    meta: [
      {
        name: "twitter:image",
        content: "https://edhiuk.org/images/logo.jpg",
      },
      { name: "twitter:title", content: "Edhi Foundation Refugees Assistance - Support Refugees" },
      { name: "twitter:description", content: "Support Edhi Foundation's Refugees Assistance services. Help provide aid and support to refugees in need." },
      { name: "keywords", content: "" },
    ],
  }}
/>
<Base>
  <!-- <--heading started here -->
  <section
    class="relative bg-[url(/images/refugee-assistance/banner-bg.jpg)] bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat pb-12 h-[400px]"
  >
    <div
      class="bg-gradient-to-r from-white to-transparent absolute inset-0 sm:bg-transparent ltr:sm:bg-gradient-to-r rtl:sm:bg-gradient-to-l"
    >
    </div>

    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-white to-transparent ltr:sm:bg-gradient-to-r rtl:sm:bg-gradient-to-l"
    >
    </div>

    <div
      class="relative mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:flex lg:h-screen lg:items-baseline pt-12 lg:px-8"
    >
      <div class="max-w-xl text-center ltr:sm:text-left rtl:sm:text-right">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold sm:text-5xl text-left font-primary">
         
Refugees 

          <strong class="block font-extrabold text-green-600"> Assistance</strong>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-lg mt-4 sm:text-xl/relaxed text-left font-roboto">
          Edhi Foundation stands with refugees, offering vital assistance and support to those seeking shelter and safety. 
        </p>

        <div class="flex md:text-center text-left pt-8">
          <a
            href="https://donate.edhiuk.org/"
            class="px-8 h-12 rounded flex items-center gap-x-3 bg-green-700 md:text-[20px] text-[16px] text-white hover:bg-[#D92319] md:px-10 md:py-2"
          >
            Donate Now
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <div class="bg-green-600 border-black p-4">
    <h1 class="text-center text-[20px] text-white pb-2 font-roboto">
      Prophet(PBUH) Said-There is no leader who closes his door to the needy, the poor, and the destitute except that God will close the door of heaven to his poverty, neediness, and destituteness.
    </h1>
    <p class="text-center text-white">(Al-Tirmidhi, hadith no: 1332) </p>
  </div>
  <!-- <--heading ended here -->
  <Donationcard programId={[48]} />

  <!-- <Donationcard programId={[2,3]} /> -->

  <!-- section 1 started here -->
  <section>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl"></div>

      <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16">
        <div class="h-64 overflow-hidden sm:h-80 lg:h-full">
          <img
            alt=""
            src="/images/refugee-assistance/refugee-assistance-01.png"
            class="h-full w-full object-fit rounded"
          />
        </div>

        <div
          class="space-y-4 text-gray-600 md:py-auto pt-0 align-middle flex flex-col justify-center"
        >
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl pb-2">
            
Support for Refugees
          </h2>

          <p class="text-[17px] font-roboto">
            Edhi Foundation extends its services to refugees from various countries who have sought shelter in Pakistan. These refugees face numerous challenges and hardships, including access to basic necessities, language barriers, and uncertainty about their future. 
          </p>
          <p class="text-[17px]">
            The Foundation is dedicated to providing them with essential assistance and support during their time of need, ensuring they receive the care and resources necessary for their well-being and stability. 
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- section 1 ended here -->
  <!-- section 2 started here -->
  <section>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl"></div>

      <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16">
        <div
          class="space-y-4 text-gray-600 md:py-auto pt-0 align-middle flex flex-col justify-center"
        >
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl pb-2">
            Basic Needs Provision 
          </h2>

          <p class="text-[17px] font-roboto">
            Edhi Foundation is committed to ensuring that refugees receive the fundamental support they require. This includes providing access to essential needs like food, shelter, and clothing. Utilizing a network of shelters and distribution centers, the Foundation works diligently to promptly address the immediate requirements of refugees, offering a source of comfort and relief in times of distress. <br><br>
            Through these efforts, Edhi Foundation aims to create a sense of stability and security for refugees, helping them navigate their challenges with dignity and support. 
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="h-64 overflow-hidden sm:h-80 lg:h-full">
          <img
            alt=""
            src="/images/refugee-assistance/refugee-assistance-02.png"
            class="h-full w-full object-fit rounded"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- section 2 ended here -->
  <!-- section 3 started here -->
  <section>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl"></div>

      <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16">
        <div class="h-64 overflow-hidden sm:h-80 lg:h-full">
          <img
            alt=""
            src="/images/refugee-assistance/refugee-assistance-03.png"
            class="h-full w-full object-fit rounded"
          />
        </div>

        <div
          class="space-y-4 text-gray-600 md:py-auto pt-0 align-middle flex flex-col justify-center"
        >
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl pb-2">
            Healthcare Services
          </h2>

          <p class="text-[17px] font-roboto">
            In addition to addressing basic needs, Edhi Foundation also provides healthcare services to refugees, including medical consultations, treatment, and access to essential medications. By offering medical assistance, the Foundation aims to promote the well-being and health of refugees, ensuring they receive the care they require. 
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="md:py-20 py-10 max-screen-w-2xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div>
      <div
        class="align-middle bg-gradient-to-br from-green-200 to-gray-50 dark:from-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-2 md:p-10 py-6 lg:p-14 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center text-center md:text-left md:justify-start md:items-start gap-8"
        style="align-items: center;"
      >
        <div class="md:w-2/5 align-middle">
          <h5
            class="text-center md:text-6xl text-3xl text-black dark:text-white font-display font-bold leading-tight"
          >
            Get Involved
          </h5>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-1 space-y-8">
          <p
            class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 md:text-2xl text-[20px] font-roboto"
          >
            Take the next step to making a difference - support Edhi
            Foundation's humanitarian efforts!
          </p>
          <div class="text-[20px] flex justify-center md:justify-start">
            <a
              href="https://donate.edhiuk.org/"
              class="h-12 px-5 rounded-md flex items-center bg-green-700 text-white"
            >
              Donate Now
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <!-- section 3 ended here -->

  <!-- section 5 started here -->

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 sm:px-6 pb-10 md:pb-20 lg:px-8">
    <!-- <h1 class="text-green-700 text-[28px] font-bold text-center">
      Mobile Mortuary    </h1> -->
    <br />
    <div class="text-center mb-4">
      <p class="md:text-[36px] text-[17px] font-bold">
        Psychosocial Support
      </p><br />
      <div class="text-left">
        <p class="text-[17px] font-roboto w-full">
          For refugees who have endured trauma and displacement, the emotional toll can be overwhelming. Edhi Foundation recognizes the importance of addressing the mental health needs of refugees and provides a range of psychosocial support services to assist them in coping with their challenges. These services include individual counseling sessions where refugees can express their feelings and concerns in a safe and supportive environment. <br /><br />In addition to individual counseling, Edhi Foundation organizes support groups where refugees can connect with others who have experienced similar struggles. These groups offer a sense of belonging and solidarity, allowing refugees to share their stories, offer mutual support, and learn coping strategies from one another. By fostering a sense of community and camaraderie, these support groups help refugees feel less isolated and alone in their journey. <br /><br
          />
          Furthermore, Edhi Foundation implements other interventions aimed at promoting resilience and well-being among refugees. This may include providing educational workshops on stress management techniques, relaxation exercises, and mindfulness practices.  <br /><br />
          By equipping refugees with practical tools and strategies to navigate their emotional challenges, the Foundation empowers them to build inner strength and resilience in the face of adversity. 
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <!-- section 5 ended here -->
  <!-- slider section started -->
  <section class="md:pb-28 pb-[230px] pt-4">
    <ServiceSlider
      heading="Refugees Assistance"
      description="Edhi Foundation stands by refugees, providing essential support and resources to help them rebuild their lives in new environments."
      img1="/images/refugee-assistance/refugee-assistance-1.jpg"
      img2="/images/refugee-assistance/refugee-assistance-2.jpg"
      img3="/images/refugee-assistance/refugee-assistance-3.jpg"
      img4="/images/refugee-assistance/refugee-assistance-4.jpg"
      img5="/images/refugee-assistance/refugee-assistance-5.jpg"
