                Edhi employs a comprehensive assessment process to identify and prioritize the needs of refugees. This involves conducting interviews, surveys, and field assessments to understand the unique challenges faced by refugees and tailor assistance accordingly. Additionally, they collaborate with local authorities and humanitarian organizations to ensure a coordinated response. 
