              <p class="p-3 text-gray-900 md:text-[17px] text-[14px]">
                Refugees can access the services offered by Edhi through various channels including refugee camps, community centers, outreach programs, and helplines. Additionally, Edhi operates mobile assistance units that reach remote or inaccessible areas to ensure that refugees receive assistance wherever they are located. 
